entry.title: Azure-Samples/app-service-baseline-implementation
entry.summary: A baseline implementation for running web applications on Azure App Service in a single region. It details guidance for designing a secure, zone-redundant, and highly available web application on Azure. The architecture exposes a public endpoint via Azure Application Gateway with WAF. It routes requests to Azure App Service through Private Link.
